3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper considers the dynamics of batteries in energy harvesting communication, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may involve multimedia applications of energy harvesting communication, such as wireless sensor networks for multimedia data transmission.
